name: A Journey of Faith A Photographers Introspective Travels by Rus Recia

metadata.name: Academia Blue
metadata.description: It was a mad dash from St. Mark’s Square trying to get to Ponte dell’Accademia before blue hour.  By the time I reached the bridge, a long line of tourists and photographers had lined up along the edge of the bridge.  I was lucky enough to squeeze my way and set up the tripod just in time for blue hour.
